dc_title_s: Saskatchewan, map showing disposition of lands
dc_description_s: Cartographic Details: Scale 1:792,000. 1 in. to 12 1/2 mi. (W 110⁰00ʹ--W 102⁰00ʹ/N 55⁰30ʹ--N 49⁰00ʹ). Relief shown by spot heights. Corrected to July 1, 1918.
